import Vue from 'vue'
import App from './App.vue'
import store from './store'
import VueRouter from 'vue-router'
import LoginPage from './components/loginPage'

Vue.config.productionTip = false
Vue.use(VueRouter)

const routes = [
  {path: '/', component: LoginPage}
]
new Vue({
  store,
  render: h => h(App),
}).$mount('#app')
